{
  "texts": [
    "Example: \"Given that we want to respect the fact that people like symmetric faces, which of these portraits is the most beautiful?",
    "Explain your thoughts and also include the notion of face symmetry. \"",
    "Sometimes, one may feel a little uncreative, not knowing how to craft a good prompt to guide the machine towards the preferred response.",
    "This is here referred to as the prompt-wise tabula-rasa problem, since it feels like one is sitting in front a \"white paper\" with no clue how to best start.",
    "In such cases, there are two prompt techniques helping us out there."
  ]
}